c: 3
v: 36
t: "To, a lõkacin da ta haife ta sai ta ce: \"Ya Ubangijina! Lalle ne nĩ, nã haife ta mace!\"KumaAllah ne Mafi sanin abin da ta haifa.\" Kuma namiji bai zama kamar mace ba. Kuma nĩ nã yi mata suna Maryamu* kuma lalle ne ni, ina nẽma mata tsari gare Ka, ita da zũriyarta daga Shaiɗan jẽfaffe"